FFFE FFA2             (    forth6809.asm):00449         VRESET   FDB   COLDSTRT
                      (    forth6809.asm):00450         
     0000             (    forth6809.asm):00451         VECTOREND  EQU   *          ; Verify vectors size, value should match $10.
